Quick and dirty to turn off the keyboard backlight

Must be istalled setuserid root

compile with:

	gcc -static thinkpad_kbd_led_off.c -o thinkpad_kbd_led_off

install with:

	# mv thinkpad_kbd_led_off <destination>
	# chown root <destination>/thinkpad_kbd_led_off
	# chmod 4555 <destination>/thinkpad_kbd_led_off


